{"tid":826230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：市民認為政府做得不足　以特首來出氣無問題","createTime":"2018-09-18T06:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T08:48:30.000Z","uid":47714,"like":3,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9d31e1756300466cf589ee721fda1035258080a4","tid":826230,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418666-20180918.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418666-20180918.htm&d=JhsCm%2BJvmlA5Pvrt6R4339U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ea0ea0f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1418666-20180918.htm&h=4180ba71\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1418666-20180918.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/videos/vfile_1418666_1_20180918133005.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fvideos%2Fvfile_1418666_1_20180918133005.mp4&d=JhsCm%2BJvmlA5Pvrt6R4339U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=474073d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/videos/vfile_1418666_1_20180918133005.mp4</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1418666_2_M_20180918120538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1418666_2_M_20180918120538.jpg&h=ae6fb8e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥稱市民認為政府做得不足　以特首來出氣無問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1418666_1_L_20180918113947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1418666_1_L_20180918113947.jpg&h=49f0cf74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥表示，市民認為政府做得不足，政府會繼續努力。（陳子麒攝）<br />\n<br />\n對於在風暴「山竹」吹襲過後，有意見認為昨日應全港停工，行政長官林鄭月娥表示，政府無機制評估停工所帶來的法律後果，以及對各行業的評估，認為政府所作的三次呼籲，僱主應諒解包容僱員未能準時上班，不要扣減人工或視作請假，她認為透過呼籲是最有效方法，不認為適合援引緊急條例。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又提到，她的呼籲是「人之常情」，自己作為18萬公務員僱主，亦作靈活安排，但未必能下達給各級公務員同事，可能內部溝通上未臻完善，又認為公務員主管應認識有關指引，當局未來亦會檢視。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，市民認為政府做得不足，政府會繼續努力，她完全能體會市民在鐵路站等了很久，感到徬徨及不滿，並以行政長官來出氣無問題，但如果因而作出無法律基礎及無對各行業評估的決定，並非行政長官負責任的做法。<br />\n<br />\n不過她說，如有嚴峻情況令公眾安全受損而需要政府有特定行為，保安局局長會作檢視今次暴風過後政府在應變善後的工作。<br />\n<br />\n至於停課方面，林鄭月娥說，停課是考慮學生安全，或因路面等情況加重交通負擔，又指雖然昨日全面停課，但很多校長及老師無停工，有回校檢視學校受損程度。"},{"pid":"32a2085bf8b6760f3b97bb723f3ef0fc7a71c5cb","tid":826230,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"有保皇狗撐腰<br />\n係唔同d既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d809ef8b83dfa9d254824876e2af6fd5e534899e","tid":826230,"uid":191527,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"出火有冇問題"},{"pid":"70e2e2b2790a840caa25a6725d621bebf7565f16","tid":826230,"uid":146535,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"佢係僱主?<br />\n佢私人攞份糧出嚟養起咁多個公務員啊"},{"pid":"7b9e127d3af91a98047834d4f4d80ec2ba26fc62","tid":826230,"uid":62226,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:05:40.000Z","msg":"我冇錯我冇錯我冇錯"},{"pid":"0442ffccf302e3aa287732372e5a6149b06f6961","tid":826230,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:06:33.000Z","msg":"出?點出呀?咁出定咁出呀?"},{"pid":"5a1c16360592588c95e95d0ea1cc8150eae38fd0","tid":826230,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:06:49.000Z","msg":"串撚到"},{"pid":"5262695327fa74cddfe5412e84e82d4f6f14ed9f","tid":826230,"uid":133319,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:07:14.000Z","msg":"怨婦"},{"pid":"2e67078db3769f1270d67010d46d3d6d22efd536","tid":826230,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T06:09:12.000Z","msg":"不過她說，如有嚴峻情況令公眾安全受損而需要政府有特定行為，保安局局長會作檢視今次暴風過後政府在應變善後的工作。<br />\n<br />\n呢句都已經有D 補獲FEEL 啦, 佢唔死撐又唔得"},{"pid":"ad0acc4b21b3ccb386f86ddf2ef62b0e04846afe","tid":826230,"uid":60271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"